    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>exhibit99-1.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EXHIBIT 99.1\n<TEXT>\n<html>\n\n<head>\n    <title>Galiano Gold Inc.: Exhibit 99.1 - Filed by newsfilecorp.com</title>\n</head>\n\n<body style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'Times New Roman';\">\n    <hr width=\"100%\" size=\"3\" color=\"black\" noshade=\"noshade\"><a name=\"page_1\"></a>\n    <div id=\"header_page_1\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"exhibit99-1xu001.jpg\"></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font style=\"color: #917837; font-size: 12pt;\">GALIANO GOLD ANNOUNCES ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING VOTING RESULTS</font></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Vancouver, British Columbia, June 2, 2022 - Galiano Gold Inc. (\"Galiano\" or the \"Company\") (TSX, NYSE American: AKG) </b>announces today that all the resolutions put to shareholders at the Company's Annual General Meeting (the \"Meeting\") held on June 2, 2022 were duly passed. The results for each of the matters voted upon at the Meeting are set out below:</p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Election of Directors</b></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The seven nominees listed in the Company's Management Information Circular dated April 27, 2022, were elected at the Meeting as directors of Galiano.</p>\n    <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 10pt;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"width: 16%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; text-align: justify;\"><b>Director Name</b></td>\n            <td style=\"width: 21%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;\"><b>Votes For</b></td>\n            <td style=\"width: 15%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;\"><b>% Votes For</b></td>\n            <td style=\"width: 19%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;\"><b>Votes Withheld</b></td>\n            <td style=\"width: 15%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;\"><b>% Votes<br>Withheld</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"width: 16%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(230, 239, 255);\">Matt Badylak</td>\n            <td style=\"width: 21%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; background-color: rgb(230, 239, 255);\">141,177,893</td>\n            <td style=\"width: 15%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; background-color: rgb(230, 239, 255);\">98.95%</td>\n            <td style=\"width: 19%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; background-color: rgb(230, 239, 255);\">1,505,005</td>\n            <td style=\"width: 15%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0.75pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right; background-color: rgb(230, 239, 255);\">1.05%</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"width: 16%; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify;\">Paul N. Wright</td>\n  